movie.title: It Takes Three
movie.description_intro: Sassy and Bella, along with their new friend Buddy, hit the road in an RV to reunite their family and save the day! There's plenty of adventure along the way, especially when they meet troublemaker kitty Jean-Clawed. Tune in and enjoy the ride!

movies.title: Who Was That Lady?
movies.summary: In order to get back into the good graces with his wife with whom he has had a misunderstanding, a young chemistry professor concocts a wild story that he is an undercover FBI agent. To help him with his story he enlists the aid of a friend who is a TV writer. The wife swallows the story and later real FBI agents and enemy spies become involved in the scheme.

movies.title: Rag Doll
movies.summary: In an attempt to escape the systemic violence in her life, inexperienced Nora Phoenix enters an MMA tournament with high hopes to save her mother's life and change hers forever. But when Nora realizes her biggest fight might not be in the ring, she must learn how to fight with her mind or risk losing everything.

movies.title: A Bennett Song Holiday
movies.summary: The unique Bennett-Song family learns the true meaning of the holidays as they solve a community crisis and adapt to big changes. Everything you want in a holiday film: love, the power of belief, laughter, tears, and new music classics.
